data.description: Great Townhome in the Ambergate community with a very Low HOA. This charming townhouse is located in a serene neighborhood, offering a peaceful and comfortable living environment. Modern design and well-maintained exterior, this gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms. All ceramic tiles on the first floor. The KITCHEN included SS appliances, granite countertops, and an eat-in dining area, there is plenty of space for family and friends. It seamlessly connects to the dining area, making it ideal for entertaining and daily living. The master suite is a private retreat, complete with a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. The full Size 2 Car and a paver driveway. Down the street, there is a great shopping/dining and grocery store. This area is a growing community, with great outdoor activities, and is close to all major Central Florida amenities.. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhouse your new home. Contact us today to schedule a showing!
